...in the future, but I
shall never forget you.

747
01:25:49,644 --> 01:25:51,077
- Sanju.
- Yes, father.

748
01:25:55,350 --> 01:25:57,318
- Deposit this Rs. 5000 in
the bank. - Yes, father.

749
01:26:02,891 --> 01:26:04,916
What are you
looking at, Anjali?

750
