- So, what? - No,
it is very expensive.

757
01:26:25,180 --> 01:26:26,579
And I don't want such
an expensive gift.

758
01:26:26,648 --> 01:26:29,014
I'll get hold of Sanju
and have it returned.

759
01:26:30,618 --> 01:26:32,245
Ratan, have you
seen Sanju?

760
01:26:32,320 --> 01:26:34,083
I saw him heading
for sunset point.

761
01:28:07,982 --> 01:28:10,450
Sanju, wake up!

762
01:28:10,518 --> 01:28:14,454
- We have to go for practice.
- Let go off me! - Get up!

763
01:28:14,522 --> 01:28:18,083
- Oh, all right.
- Come quickly.

764
01:28:37,245 --> 01:28:39,213
Where are the rest?

765
01:28:42,250 --> 01:28:44,275
Sanju is here too!

766
01:28:44,585 --> 01:28:47,816
If he comes once, he takes
a break for several days.

767
01:28:48,990 --> 01:28:52,323
- Have you taken the full round
today? - One hour 10 minutes.

768
01:28:53,928 --> 01:28:58,058
If this was the race,
I would have won it.

769
01:28:59,033 --> 01:29:04,061
You would have won it last year.
But, Shekhar forged ahead

770
01:29:04,138 --> 01:29:07,505
It is the last few seconds that
decide the defeat and victory.

771
01:29:07,575 --> 01:29:11,170
Whatever it may be,
everyone believes that...

772
01:29:11,245 --> 01:29:14,976
...only you can defeat
Shekhar... It's true.

773
01:29:17,085 --> 01:29:19,645
So much hope can make
a person nervous.

774
01:29:21,356 --> 01:29:25,087
Especially father.
He keeps dreaming of...

775
01:29:25,159 --> 01:29:26,956
...my victory and
Shekhar's defeat.

776
01:29:28,663 --> 01:29:30,961
He wants to buy an
Italian cycle for me.

777
01:29:31,032 --> 01:29:34,092
- It costs Rs. 20, 000.
- 20, 000!

778
01:29:38,473 --> 01:29:44,105
I fear that if I don't win
father will heartbroken.

779
01:30:10,471 --> 01:30:13,133
This training is very good.
We ought to take it too.

780
01:30:13,274 --> 01:30:16,903
Okay! With such training,
you'll surely beat Shekhar.

781
01:30:16,978 --> 01:30:19,538
We have seen nothing.
You may continue.

782
01:30:27,288 --> 01:30:29,256
Sanju meets me very
rarely these days.

783
01:30:29,323 --> 01:30:32,451
