Don't ever forget me, Sanju.

786
01:31:02,423 --> 01:31:04,391
Who is accompanying her?

787
01:31:09,730 --> 01:31:11,322
What is she doing
with a boy from Model?

788
01:31:26,314 --> 01:31:28,339
Do you know Devika?

789
01:31:28,549 --> 01:31:31,347
She is from Queens College
and is of our class.

790
01:31:31,419 --> 01:31:35,947
How dare a stupid localite of
Model College, befriend her?

791
