792
01:31:47,768 --> 01:31:49,668
And I am not a bastard
but you are.

793
01:31:56,711 --> 01:31:58,679
Come on, jerk!

794
01:32:39,020 --> 01:32:41,045
What happened?

795
01:32:41,122 --> 01:32:43,647
Sir, he is attempting to
ruin a respectable girl.

796
01:32:43,724 --> 01:32:46,420
Which girl?

797
01:32:46,494 --> 01:32:48,359
She is from Queens College
and she is my family friend.

798
01:32:48,529 --> 01:32:51,123
- What nonsense!
- Shut up! - Get lost!

799
