- What happened, Sanju?
- Quiet! You're spoiling him.

803
01:33:21,562 --> 01:33:22,756
He must have
started the fight.

804
01:33:22,930 --> 01:33:26,093
Don't interfere in my matters.
I don't need your sermon.

805
01:33:33,074 --> 01:33:36,100
I'm glad to have found you.

806
01:33:36,177 --> 01:33:38,111
I have something
important to discuss.

807
01:33:38,179 --> 01:33:39,578
Let's go sit somewhere.

808
01:33:39,647 --> 01:33:41,581
Not now as I have to
go for rehearsals.

809
01:33:41,649 --> 01:33:44,379
Next Sunday there's
a dance competition.

810
01:33:44,452 --> 01:33:46,647
...in which we're participating
with Rajput College.

811
01:33:46,721 --> 01:33:48,120
Shekhar is also participating.

812
01:33:51,726 --> 01:33:52,852
Right now, I want to
tell you about myself.

813
01:33:57,898 --> 01:33:59,866
Devika, hurry up.
The bus is leaving.

814
01:34:03,070 --> 01:34:05,868
I'm off now, we'll meet
at the dance competition.

815
01:34:05,940 --> 01:34:09,205
- You are in the Xavier's
team, aren't you? - Yes.

816
01:34:09,977 --> 01:34:12,207
