full of youth."

821
01:34:48,549 --> 01:34:53,316
"Because of us
is this world."

822
01:35:14,909 --> 01:35:18,811
"Where ever you see in
the darkness of the night."

823
01:35:18,879 --> 01:35:21,814
"Or you search in
the morning light."

824
01:35:30,524 --> 01:35:33,960
"We all are seen, no
one can be are equal."

825
01:35:38,999 --> 01:35:41,729
"The world is
because of us."

826
01:35:50,010 --> 01:35:54,071
Let's see how many points
the judges have given them.

827
01:35:54,148 --> 01:35:57,743
After the spectacular
performance by Xavier's...

828
01:35:57,818 --> 01:36:01,083
