wonderful, Sanjay.

883
01:45:53,547 --> 01:45:57,005
I didn't know that
you were so great.

884
01:45:57,084 --> 01:46:00,520
You ought to get the first
prize for what you did.

885
01:46:01,555 --> 01:46:04,023
I worked very hard...

886
01:46:04,091 --> 01:46:06,525
...but I must have lacked
something to have missed it.

887
01:46:06,593 --> 01:46:10,029
You didn't understand.
Anyway, forget it.

888
01:46:10,097 --> 01:46:12,531
I'll be there at Malroadat
approximately 8 O'clock.

889
01:46:12,599 --> 01:46:14,533
All right, I'll see
you at eight.

890
01:46:20,574 --> 01:46:23,042
- Where are you coming from?
- The doctor's clinic.

891
01:46:23,110 --> 01:46:25,044
- Why?
- I've got fever.

892
01:46:25,112 --> 01:46:28,548
You ought to rest.
Why are you loitering around?

893
01:46:28,615 --> 01:46:30,048
I'm on my way home.

894
01:46:31,585 --> 01:46:34,053
Anjali, could I get a
car from your garage?

895
01:46:36,590 --> 01:46:38,057
Where do you have to go?

896
01:46:38,592 --> 01:46:42,050
Devika's coming to meet me today
and I'll have to drop her back.

897
01:46:42,596 --> 01:46:45,064
- You can take it.
- Thank you!

898
01:46:46,600 --> 01:46:50,559
Oh Anjali, sometimes I feel
as though I am in a dream.

899
01:46:51,605 --> 01:46:55,564
Frankly, I'd never contemplated
that a rich girl like Devika...

900
01:46:55,642 --> 01:46:57,075
...would fall in love with me.

901
01:46:57,144 --> 01:46:59,578
- Sanju, may I say something?
- Sure.

902
01:46:59,646 --> 01:47:02,080
Are you sure that
Devika really loves you?

903
01:47:02,149 --> 01:47:05,084
I mean, some girls
mistake their feelings.

904
01:47:05,152 --> 01:47:08,087
No, Anjali. It is not a case
of mistaken feelings.

905
01:47:08,155 --> 01:47:10,589
Have you told her
all about yourself?

906
01:47:10,657 --> 01:47:12,090
You mean, the fact
that I'm from Model?

907
01:47:12,626 --> 01:47:15,094
She realised that on the day
of the dance competition.

908
01:47:15,162 --> 01:47:17,596
And she is aware that no
wealthy boy studies at Model.

909
01:47:17,664 --> 01:47:20,098
That is why she lost her
pallor when she saw you.

910
01:47:20,167 --> 01:47:21,099
What!

911
01:47:21,168 --> 01:47:24,103
The moment she realised you were
from Model and not Xavier's...

912
01:47:24,171 --> 01:47:27,607
What nonsense! If that was the
case, why would she call me?

913
01:47:27,674 --> 01:47:30,108
Why would she praise my dance
and come to meet me today?

914
01:47:30,644 --> 01:47:32,612
All girls are not the same.

915
01:47:32,679 --> 01:47:34,112
Devika is not a gold digger.

916
01:47:34,648 --> 01:47:37,116
She likes me.
She loves Sanju.

917
01:47:37,184 --> 01:47:40,119
Don't be naive, Sanju.
She doesn't love you.

918
01:47:40,187 --> 01:47:41,620
Why are you talking nonsense?

919
01:47:41,688 --> 01:47:44,623
Instead of being happy for me,
you're trying to create doubts.

920
01:47:44,691 --> 01:47:46,124
I'm not creating doubts.

921
01:47:46,193 --> 01:47:48,627
I'm trying to prevent you
from making a mistake.

922
01:47:49,162 --> 01:47:53,121
I don't want you
to be deeply hurt.

923
01:47:53,667 --> 01:47:57,125
Anjali, I don't like this
pointless talk from you.

924
01:47:57,204 --> 01:48:01,140
