I'll never speak to you again.

925
01:48:01,208 --> 01:48:02,641
I won't meet you either.

926
01:48:06,680 --> 01:48:08,147
Neither do I want
to see you again.

927
01:48:10,183 --> 01:48:13,641
Sanju, you shouldn't speak
to Anjali in this manner.

928
01:48:13,720 --> 01:48:16,154
