01:51:20,874 --> 01:51:23,843
You said that money
didn't matter to you.

953
01:51:23,910 --> 01:51:25,844
You said that it
wouldn't matter...

954
01:51:25,912 --> 01:51:27,846
...if I didn't have
anything in the future.

955
01:51:29,382 --> 01:51:30,849
So it was a lie.

956
01:51:33,386 --> 01:51:35,854
A person who has started
out with a lie...

957
01:51:35,922 --> 01:51:38,857
...has no right to
call anyone else a liar.

958
01:51:39,392 --> 01:51:40,859
I admit that I lied.

959
01:51:41,394 --> 01:51:44,852
But I did it only to
disguise my poverty.

960
01:51:44,931 --> 01:51:46,865
And you lied to
disguise your deceit.

961
01:51:47,400 --> 01:51:49,868
Until yesterday I was Thapar's
son, so you approved of me.

962
01:51:49,936 --> 01:51:53,372
And now that I am an ordinary
man's son, I disgust you.

963
01:51:53,907 --> 01:51:55,875
That's because you
want a rich boyfriend.

964
01:51:55,942 --> 01:51:59,378
If not Thapar's son, Malhotra's
son Shekhar will do...

965
01:51:59,446 --> 01:52:01,880
...regardless of his bad
character. Isn't that right?

966
01:52:01,948 --> 01:52:03,381
Yes, that's it.

967
01:52:27,440 --> 01:52:29,908
- What is the matter, Devika?
- Nothing.

968
01:52:33,446 --> 01:52:36,904
Hey Jerk, I've left you
Rs 10 at your cafe.

969
01:52:36,983 --> 01:52:38,917
Take it from your
champion brother.

970
01:52:47,961 --> 01:52:49,929
Why are you hiding
your face now?

971
01:52:49,996 --> 01:52:52,931
She wouldn't even
care to spit on it.

972
01:52:52,999 --> 01:52:55,433
Keep within the limits of your
status and you'll be happy.

973
01:52:55,969 --> 01:52:57,436
Go and take
the 10 rupees.

974
01:53:15,488 --> 01:53:17,956
Beat him!
Don't spare him!

975
01:53:23,496 --> 01:53:24,463
Pick him up.

976
01:53:28,501 --> 01:53:29,968
You woo a girl, eh?

977
01:53:30,503 --> 01:53:31,970
You're Model's hero, eh?

978
01:53:37,510 --> 01:53:40,968
You stupid localite! How dare
you woo a girl from Queens?

979
01:53:43,516 --> 01:53:44,983
You've become too
big for your boots.

980
01:53:45,051 --> 01:53:47,986
Didn't I tell you that I did not
want any tricks from you?

981
01:53:51,524 --> 01:53:52,491
Bastard!

982
01:53:57,530 --> 01:54:01,489
Don't spare him!
Break his bones!

983
01:54:02,535 --> 01:54:04,002
Will you approach
a girl again?

984
01:54:04,070 --> 01:54:07,005
What do you think of yourself,
you stupid localite.

985
01:55:07,600 --> 01:55:10,068
Release him carefully.

986
01:55:31,624 --> 01:55:32,591
Get lost!

987
01:55:36,129 --> 01:55:37,596
Both of you go home.

988
01:55:38,631 --> 01:55:39,598
Come along!

989
01:55:41,634 --> 01:55:44,102
I've warned you not to
interfere with these boys.

990
01:55:45,138 --> 01:55:48,107
You're still on
Devika's case.

991
01:55:48,641 --> 01:55:51,610
Mark my words, this fight
will blow out of proportion.

992
01:55:52,145 --> 01:55:55,603
And, if I hadn't arrived, they
would have broken all your bones.

993
01:55:55,682 --> 01:55:58,116
Hey! I could have
handled them alone.

994
01:55:58,184 --> 01:56:01,620
Who asked you to interfere? Don't
pretend to be a great saviour.

995
01:56:01,688 --> 01:56:04,623
Oh! So you're very strong, eh?
Come on.

996
01:56:04,691 --> 01:56:07,626
Ratan, I warn you.
Don't challenge me.

997
01:56:07,694 --> 01:56:09,628
- Are you afraid?
- Hey!

998
01:56:31,684 --> 01:56:34,653
I gave you Rs 5000 to
deposit at the bank...

999
01:56:34,721 --> 01:56:36,154
...but this shows
only Rs 1000.

1000
01:56:36,222 --> 01:56:38,156
Father, you didn't
give me any money.

1001
01:56:38,691 --> 01:56:40,158
Ah yes!
I had given it to Sanju.

1002
01:56:44,697 --> 01:56:51,660
Sanju, I... What's this?
You've fought again!

1003
01:56:54,707 --> 01:56:58,165
I gave you Rs 5000 to
deposit at the bank.

1004
01:56:58,244 --> 01:57:00,178
But this shows
only Rs 1000.

1005
01:57:02,215 --> 01:57:06,174
How much did you deposit?
Why don't you answer?

1006
01:57:07,720 --> 01:57:08,687
Rs 1000.

1007
01:57:09,222 --> 01:57:12,191
1000? What about the
remaining Rs 4000?

1008
01:57:13,726 --> 01:57:15,193
I spent it.

1009
01:57:16,229 --> 01:57:21,189
Spent it! What did you spend
on? Why don't you tell me?

1010
01:57:22,735 --> 01:57:26,694
It wasn't a paltry sum that you
spent with no explanations!

1011
01:57:27,740 --> 01:57:29,207
Did you gamble?

1012
01:57:29,742 --> 01:57:33,200
Where is the Rs 4000?
Tell me!

1013
01:57:33,746 --> 01:57:37,705
I can't tell you, but I
will return the money.

1014
01:57:39,752 --> 01:57:44,712
I'm working day and night in
order to buy a cycle for Ratan.

1015
01:57:44,791 --> 01:57:47,225
And you blow it up
without a second thought.

1016
01:57:47,293 --> 01:57:48,726
Get out!

1017
01:57:49,262 --> 01:57:54,723
Get out! And don't
you dare to return!

1018
01:58:59,332 --> 01:59:03,792
Father, there's no need to go
to Delhi to buy a new cycle.

1019
01:59:03,870 --> 01:59:05,303
It will be an
unnecessary expense.

1020
01:59:05,371 --> 01:59:06,804
Besides, my old cycle
will suffice.

1021
01:59:07,340 --> 01:59:08,807
Don't worry about it.

1022
01:59:09,842 --> 01:59:13,300
- I'll be back by 11 p. M.
- All right, father.

1023
01:59:15,848 --> 01:59:19,807
Father, please forgive Sanju.

1024
01:59:19,886 --> 01:59:23,322
I'll reason with him.
It won't happen again.

1025
01:59:23,389 --> 01:59:24,822
Allow him to come home.

1026
01:59:29,862 --> 01:59:30,829
Let's go.

1027
01:59:55,888 --> 01:59:59,847
Sanju, father has gone to Delhi
and he will return at 11 p. M.

1028
02:00:01,394 --> 02:00:04,363
I apologised on your behalf
and he has forgiven you.

1029
02:00:04,430 --> 02:00:05,863
Come home now.

1030
02:00:07,900 --> 02:00:12,860
I know that you're angry with
me. I shouldn't have hit you.

1031
02:00:12,939 --> 02:00:16,375
Next time, I will ignore the fact
that you are my older brother.

1032
02:00:17,410 --> 02:00:20,379
And I don't need your pity.
Here's your blanket.

1033
02:00:20,913 --> 02:00:24,371
It wasn't me, but Anjali, who
covered you with this blanket.

1034
02:00:26,919 --> 02:00:28,386
Anyway, I'm sorry.

1035
02:01:13,966 --> 02:01:17,424
Yesterday, your fighter
and you were lucky...

1036
02:01:17,503 --> 02:01:19,437
...because I wasn't present.

1037
02:01:19,972 --> 02:01:21,439
What will you do today?

1038
02:01:21,507 --> 02:01:24,442
I'll give you the same treatment
that I gave your friends.

1039
02:01:29,982 --> 02:01:32,951
You will have to be
taught a lesson.

1040
02:01:37,990 --> 02:01:39,457
Let's see who teaches
whom a lesson?

1041
02:03:08,581 --> 02:03:11,550
- Ratan's met with an accident.
- What! How did it happen?

1042
02:03:11,617 --> 02:03:13,050
I don't know...

1043
02:03:13,119 --> 02:03:15,553
...but it seems that he fell
off the cliff with his cycle.

1044
02:03:15,621 --> 02:03:18,556
He has been taken to the
Government hospital... Hurry!

1045
02:03:32,104 --> 02:03:34,572
Doctor, I am Ratan's
younger brother.

1046
02:03:35,107 --> 02:03:37,575
What was... How is he?
What has happened to him?

1047
02:03:37,643 --> 02:03:39,577
- Where is your father?
- He has gone to Delhi.

1048
02:03:39,645 --> 02:03:41,078
- When will he return?
- Tonight.

1049
02:03:41,147 --> 02:03:42,580
Bring him along as
soon as he returns.

1050
02:03:42,648 --> 02:03:44,582
But, doctor... What's
happened to him?

1051
02:03:45,117 --> 02:03:48,086
The operation is badly needed.
I don't have the time to spare.

1052
02:04:08,641 --> 02:04:11,610
No one can
defeat Ratan now.

1053
02:04:16,148 --> 02:04:17,615
Call Ratan.

1054
02:04:26,158 --> 02:04:27,625
- Father...
- What is the matter?

1055
02:04:31,163 --> 02:04:34,132
I have forgiven you...

1056
02:04:34,200 --> 02:04:36,134
...but don't repeat
this mistake again.

1057
02:04:36,202 --> 02:04:39,638
Go... Go and fetch Ratan.

1058
02:04:40,172 --> 02:04:43,630
Ratan has met with an accident.
He is in the hospital.

1059
02:05:06,699 --> 02:05:08,166
The state in which
he was brought...

1060
02:05:08,234 --> 02:05:09,667
...required an
emergency operation.

1061
02:05:12,204 --> 02:05:14,672
He's still in coma.

1062
02:05:20,212 --> 02:05:22,180
I do not wish to
raise false hopes.

1063
02:05:24,216 --> 02:05:25,683
His condition
is very critical.

1064
02:06:51,303 --> 02:06:53,271
Be brave.

1065
02:06:55,307 --> 02:06:56,274
Yes.

1066
02:06:59,311 --> 02:07:01,779
Last night,
I fought with Ratan.

1067
02:07:02,314 --> 02:07:08,275
This morning he came to pacify
me, but I didn't respond.

1068
02:07:09,321 --> 02:07:10,788
If anything happens to him...

1069
02:07:17,329 --> 02:07:18,796
What will happen now?

1070
02:07:20,332 --> 02:07:26,293
How will father survive?
He means everything to father.

1071
02:07:27,339 --> 02:07:29,807
He... and you too.

1072
02:08:25,397 --> 02:08:32,360
"If ever you got annoyed
with me and went away..."

1073
02:08:40,412 --> 02:08:47,875
"...I had never expected
to miss you so much."

1074
02:09:30,963 --> 02:09:37,425
"I could never walk even
two steps without you."

1075
02:09:38,470 --> 02:09:44,932
"Yet in my innocence,
I always thought...

1076
02:09:46,478 --> 02:09:53,441
"...you will never leave me."

1077
02:10:01,493 --> 02:10:08,956
"I had never expected
to miss you so much."

1078
02:10:58,550 --> 02:11:06,013
"If ever you got annoyed
with me and went away...

1079
02:11:25,577 --> 02:11:28,546
Ratan has regained
consciousness.

1080
02:11:28,614 --> 02:11:32,550
I'm returning from the hospital.
He's fine. He even spoke to me.

1081
02:11:32,618 --> 02:11:36,054
The Lord has
answered our prayers!

1082
02:12:09,121 --> 02:12:11,089
What if he tells the police?

1083
02:12:11,623 --> 02:12:15,081
I warned you to tell the
principal, but you...

1084
02:12:16,628 --> 02:12:18,596
It would have been
better if he had died.

1085
02:12:24,636 --> 02:12:29,596
- Water...
- I'll get it.

1086
02:12:49,161 --> 02:12:54,121
If you tell anything to anyone,
the consequences won't be good.

1087
02:13:07,679 --> 02:13:11,638
What was he
doing here, so late?

1088
02:13:12,684 --> 02:13:13,651
Tell me.

1089
02:13:15,687 --> 02:13:19,646
You are keeping something
from me. What is the matter?

1090
02:13:21,693 --> 02:13:24,161
- Tell me.
- I'll tell you.

1091
02:13:27,699 --> 02:13:31,658
Sanju, do you think that
I'll be alright for the race?

1092
02:13:33,705 --> 02:13:35,172
Drink your medicine.

1093
02:13:38,710 --> 02:13:40,678
The race will take place
on the 24th of next month.

1094
02:13:41,713 --> 02:13:46,173
Even if I get a week's
practice, it will suffice.

1095
02:13:46,718 --> 02:13:48,686
Isn't that right?

1096
02:13:50,222 --> 02:13:53,191
Don't worry, you'll be fine.

1097
02:13:54,726 --> 02:13:56,193
There's still a month
and a half left.

1098
02:13:56,261 --> 02:13:59,196
Yes, there's a month
and a half left.

1099
02:14:00,732 --> 02:14:02,199
This time, I will defeat him.

1100
02:14:03,735 --> 02:14:08,195
Sanju, I will surely
defeat him this time.

1101
02:14:08,740 --> 02:14:11,208
I won't spare him.

1102
02:14:14,746 --> 02:14:16,213
I'll defeat him.

1103
02:14:25,257 --> 02:14:28,226
Come along, Sanju.
Hurry up, Ghode, let's go.

1104
02:14:38,770 --> 02:14:40,237
Shall we go?

1105
02:14:43,775 --> 02:14:46,243
Anjali, I will participate
in the cycle race this year.

1106
02:14:46,311 --> 02:14:50,247
- What! Are you serious?
- Yes.

1107
02:14:50,782 --> 02:14:53,250
I might not be able to
take Ratan's place...

1108
02:14:53,785 --> 02:14:57,243
...but it's the least
I can do for father.

1109
02:14:57,789 --> 02:15:02,249
Do your best, Sanju.
I'm with you all the way.

1110
02:15:54,846 --> 02:15:58,304
Idiot, you are taking advantage
of her feelings for you!

1111
02:16:44,896 --> 02:16:46,363
What is the matter?

1112
02:16:51,903 --> 02:16:53,871
Anjali, you might
consider it strange...

1113
02:16:54,906 --> 02:16:57,875
...but I'd like to tell you
what I have been feeling...

1114
02:16:57,943 --> 02:16:59,376
...these last few days.

1115
02:16:59,911 --> 02:17:00,878
What?

1116
02:17:01,913 --> 02:17:04,381
I have always considered
you as my closest friend.

1117
02:17:07,919 --> 02:17:10,387
But... I have grown
to love you now.

1118
02:17:48,960 --> 02:17:50,427
You'll be perfectly alright
in another 3 or 4 weeks.

1119
02:17:50,962 --> 02:17:53,430
Until then, take care that you
don't put too much weight...

1120
02:17:53,498 --> 02:17:54,931
...on this leg.

1121
02:18:02,974 --> 02:18:04,441
Don't be dejected.

1122
02:18:05,977 --> 02:18:07,444
It is destiny.

1123
02:18:08,980 --> 02:18:11,448
It doesn't matter that you can't
take part in the race tomorrow.

1124
02:18:12,984 --> 02:18:16,943
Without you, Shekhar's victory
will be meaningless anyway.

1125
02:18:31,002 --> 02:18:33,971
It is Ratan's cycle. Only a
little work remains to be done.

1126
02:18:34,506 --> 02:18:36,474
Tomorrow is the race...

1127
02:18:36,541 --> 02:18:38,975
...and Sanju wants to use
this cycle for the race.

1128
02:18:45,016 --> 02:18:46,483
What is the matter, Kalpana?

1129
02:18:48,019 --> 02:18:51,477
Aren't you aware
of Ratan's grief?

1130
02:18:54,025 --> 02:18:57,984
He had worked very hard to
participate in this race.

1131
02:18:58,530 --> 02:19:01,988
And now...
He is not in this race.

1132
02:19:04,035 --> 02:19:07,493
And Sanju is responsible
for all of it.

1133
02:19:07,572 --> 02:19:09,005
- Sanju!
- Yes.

1134
02:19:09,074 --> 02:19:12,009
If he hadn't messed
around with Shekhar...

1135
02:19:12,077 --> 02:19:14,511
...Shekhar and his
friends wouldn't...

1136
02:19:15,046 --> 02:19:16,513
What did they do?

1137
02:19:18,049 --> 02:19:22,008
Anjali, please don't
disclose this to anyone.

1138
02:19:22,087 --> 02:19:24,021
Ratan forbade me to do so.

1139
02:19:24,089 --> 02:19:27,024
Please, Anjali,
do it for my sake.

1140
02:20:10,101 --> 02:20:12,569
- Why didn't you tell me?
- What?

1141
02:20:12,637 --> 02:20:14,070
You know perfectly well.

1142
02:20:15,106 --> 02:20:20,066
Shekhar & his friends attempted
to kill you and you kept mum?!

1143
02:20:22,614 --> 02:20:26,573
Ratan, you aren't aware of what
father and I have been through.

1144
02:20:27,619 --> 02:20:29,086
We nearly lost you.

1145
02:20:36,127 --> 02:20:37,594
It's my fault.

1146
02:20:39,631 --> 02:20:42,099
You became the target for
Shekhar's enmity towards me.

1147
02:20:50,141 --> 02:20:51,608
- Where are you going?
- Let me go!

1148
02:20:51,676 --> 02:20:53,109
- Let go of the rod!
- Let me go!

1149
02:20:53,178 --> 02:20:54,110
Leave it!

1150
02:21:00,151 --> 02:21:04,611
Do you want to know why I kept
mum? Listen carefully.

1151
02:21:05,156 --> 02:21:09,115
When I came to my senses,
I noticed that you had changed.

1152
02:21:10,161 --> 02:21:12,129
You had changed completely.

1153
02:21:12,197 --> 02:21:14,631
You had begun to realise
your responsibilities.

1154
02:21:16,167 --> 02:21:19,625
You learned to appreciate
me... and father.

1155
02:21:21,172 --> 02:21:25,131
You became closer to
us. I was very happy.

1156
02:21:26,177 --> 02:21:35,142
For your happiness, I couldn't
care if anything happened to me.

1157
02:21:51,202 --> 02:21:52,669
I have troubled
you so much.

1158
02:21:54,205 --> 02:21:56,173
And yet you have never
said anything to me.

1159
02:21:57,208 --> 02:21:58,675
Then leave
everything behind.

1160
02:21:58,743 --> 02:22:00,677
I have prepared the
new cycle for you.

1161
02:22:00,745 --> 02:22:03,680
Take it and try your best
at the race tomorrow.

1162
02:22:08,219 --> 02:22:11,188
The brave sportsmen have
set off for their destination.

1163
02:22:11,256 --> 02:22:14,692
A 50 km cycle race.

1164
02:22:14,759 --> 02:22:16,192
From the stadium
to Pykara junction.

1165
02:22:16,261 --> 02:22:19,196
...then a 20 km passage
through Baramulla Hills...

1166
02:22:19,264 --> 02:22:21,698
...to the highest point.

1167
02:22:29,240 --> 02:22:30,707
'We are as good
as anyone' - Model.

1168
02:22:41,753 --> 02:22:43,220
The cyclists are
passing through.

1169
02:22:43,288 --> 02:22:44,721
It remains to be seen...

1170
02:22:44,789 --> 02:22:46,723
...who crosses the dangerous
terrain of Baramulla.

1171
02:22:58,770 --> 02:23:00,237
"Baramulla Hills"

1172
02:23:58,329 --> 02:24:01,787
I'm Rakesh Sharma reporting
from check post 2 at Pillar Rock.

1173
02:24:03,334 --> 02:24:06,792
The first cyclists have
reached Pillar Rock.

1174
02:24:06,871 --> 02:24:08,805
In the lead is Shekhar
Malhotra from Rajput College.

1175
02:24:18,349 --> 02:24:21,318
In fifth place is Sanjaylal
Sharma from Model College.

1176
02:24:59,390 --> 02:25:00,857
Be careful,
or you might fall!

1177
02:25:03,895 --> 02:25:06,864
- Come along.
- The jerk is losing air.

1178
02:25:56,447 --> 02:26:00,907
I was bound by my
promise to Ratan...

1179
02:26:00,985 --> 02:26:02,919
...but I won't spare you now.

1180
02:26:07,959 --> 02:26:10,928
Because of you, my brother is not
participating in today's race.

1181
02:26:16,467 --> 02:26:18,935
I'll see how you are
able to finish this race.

1182
02:26:19,003 --> 02:26:22,939
Get lost, jerk! I'll see
how you try to stop me.

1183
02:26:42,493 --> 02:26:43,960
You hit my brother.

1184
02:26:45,496 --> 02:26:46,963
This is Ratan's reply.

1185
02:27:03,514 --> 02:27:06,972
You won't let me
finish the race, eh?

1186
02:27:11,522 --> 02:27:13,990
They've gone ahead!

1187
02:27:14,525 --> 02:27:17,494
Shekhar, you go ahead.
We'll take care of him.

1188
02:27:17,562 --> 02:27:18,995
Don't set him free.

1189
02:27:19,530 --> 02:27:20,497
